# Simple URL Shortener

A simple URL shortener that can be managed via a simple RESTful API.

[![CI Status](https://github.com/Cakasim/shortener/workflows/CI/badge.svg?branch=develop)](https://github.com/Cakasim/shortener/actions)
[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/Cakasim/shortener.svg?branch=develop)](https://travis-ci.org/Cakasim/shortener)
[![Coverage Status](https://coveralls.io/repos/github/Cakasim/shortener/badge.svg?branch=develop)](https://coveralls.io/github/Cakasim/shortener?branch=develop)
[![LICENSE](https://img.shields.io/github/license/Cakasim/shortener.svg)](LICENSE)

## Install

```bash
# Clone sources from GitHub
git clone https://github.com/Cakasim/shortener.git

# Build JavaScript files
npm run build

# Create .env file
cp .env.example .env
```

Finally, configure your environment in `.env` file.

## Usage

```bash
npm run start
```
